  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for tiff",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for tiff fixes the following issues\n\nSecurity issues:\n\n- CVE-2025-8851: libtiff: LibTIFF Stack-based buffer overflow (bsc#1248278).\n- CVE-2026-4775: signed integer overflow in the `putcontig8bitYCbCr44tile` function (bsc#1260411).\n\nNon security issue:\n\n- QGIS can't export with GDAL- LERC codec, LERC library not found anywhere in the system (bsc#1257123).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
